Package: ShinyAsyncTools
Type: Package
Title: Tools for message passing between async processes in shiny
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ian Fellows
Maintainer: Ian Fellows <ian@fellstat.com>
Description: This package provides tools that let you update a shiny UI from within a child process (e.g. future). Examples are procided showing how to perform useful tasks such as: updating reactive values from within future, progress bars for long running async tasks, and inturrupting async tasks based on user input.
Imports: R6, shiny, txtq
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
